profile:
Providing customers with quality building, roofing, landscaping and masonry materials required to do the job right for over 80 years. Family run and owned for 4 generations, we have the experienced staff that can assist professional tradespersons and first time ‘do-it yourselfers’ alike.  Serving Oshawa, Whitby and the surrounding areas of Durham and beyond.

From pavers and block, to shingles and steel roofing.  We have what you need and provide the absolute best customer service in the region.  We have the right products to meet your needs including aggregates, insulation, geotextiles, tools (shovels, rippers, hammers, levels, knives), trowels, floats, screeds, flagstone, sills, culvert, drain pipe, sealers, forming tubes and much more!
